      <label class="med-gray h5 mb2 block">Instructor</label>
      <div class="flex underline-link mb3">
        <div class="flex-none mr3">
            <img width="80" src="https://hackdesign.imgix.net/curators/daveobrien@2x.jpg?ixlib=rails-2.1.4&dpr=2&w=80&h=80&fit=crop&fm=jpeg&auto=format&mask=ellipse&s=dc9a51672d7025c68627a6f880c40fa7" alt="Daveobrien@2x.jpg?ixlib=rails 2.1" />
        </div>
        <div class="flex-auto">
          <h5 class="h3 mt0 mb1 regular dark-blue">Dave O Brien</h5>
          <h5 class="h4 mt0 mb1 med-gray regular">
              Designer, 
              <a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com">Twitter</a>
          </h5>
          <p class="med-gray">I'm a creative from Ireland who currently works as a designer at Twitter. I enjoy dreaming up ideas, fleshing them out and building them to fruition. When I want to make my designs dynamic I breath life into them with Quartz Composer and add any additional post flourishes in After Effects. The best way to reach me is on <a href="https://www.twitter.com/davidobrien" target="_blank">Twitter</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>


